---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy | Ochre & Chrome" description="Privacy policy for Ochre & Chrome.">
  <main class="legal-page">
    <a href="/" class="oc-brand">Ochre <span>&amp;</span> Chrome</a>
    <p class="oc-kicker">Privacy</p>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>
      Ochre & Chrome is a static editorial interiors website. At this stage, the site does not
      provide account creation, checkout, or an active newsletter signup flow.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you contact us by email at hello@ochreandchrome.com, we may receive the information you
      choose to include in that message and use it only to respond to your request.
    </p>
    <p>
      The site loads fonts from Google Fonts. Your browser may connect to Google-operated servers
      to retrieve those font files. Product affiliate links are not active until verified partner
      destinations are added.
    </p>
    <p>
      Required legal operator details, jurisdiction-specific privacy disclosures, cookie language,
      and any future analytics or newsletter provider terms must be confirmed before launch.
    </p>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
